txt.en: You have encountered many Corsairs while battling through Tarlang's Crown, all of whom have been eager to test their blades against you.\n\nTheir numbers grow swiftly as more ships make landfall in Edhellond and south of Dol Amroth, and they must be stopped if any defence is to be maintained.
You have defeated many Corsairs in Tarlang's Crown.
Corsairs comprise the majority of Azruthor's forces in Tarlang's Crown, and their fondness for ale and combat makes them all the more dangerous.
Corsairs can be found throughout Tarlang's Crown.\n\nYou have encountered numerous Corsairs and should defeat them before their numbers can grow even greater.

You have defeated many of the Corsairs in Tarlang's Crown. Although their numbers are constantly bolstered by their ships in the Bay of Belfalas, you have dealt a strong blow against Azruthor's forces.
